- **Required before v0.7.0 and v0.8.0** — nodes must be able to follow multiple chains from multiple hubs before bridging and trading can work

### v0.7.0 — Bridge Basics
- Cross-chain bridge (benefits from faster sync and propagation, requires v0.6.3 for multi-island awareness)

### v0.8.0 — Inter-Chain Trading Basics
- Inter-chain trading (benefits from optimized P2P for cross-chain communication, requires v0.6.3 for multi-island following)

